(226, 80, '2014-01-18 09:52:25', '2014-01-18 14:52:25', '<h1>2017 Benefit Information</h1>\r\n2017 benefit information is here! See below for all of the 2017 benefit enrollment/change information. If you have any questions concerning these forms please contact <a href="mailto:cbrown@sequenceqcs.com" target="_blank">Carrie Brown</a> (HR).\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9-2017-Open-Enrollment-Presentation.pdf">2017 Sequence Open Enrollment Presentation</a>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Open Enrollment Meeting Recording" style="fancy"]GoToMeeting Event Recording of 2017 Open Enrollment Meeting\r\n[embed]https://youtu.be/b60J1qW_0eg[/embed]\r\n[/su_spoiler]</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Benefits At A Glance (BAAG)</strong></span>\r\n\r\nThe link below provides an overview of the benefits offered by Sequence Inc.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1-BAAG-2017.pdf">Sequence 2017 BAAG</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Fidelity 401k</strong></span>\r\n\r\nLinks and documentation\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title="Netbenefits" href="https://nb.fidelity.com/public/nb/default/home">401k NetBenefits Link</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/DS-Fidelity-Enrollment-Guide-7-16-15-2.pdf">Fidelity Enrollment Guide</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/a-NBAdvisorBrochure.pdf">Fidelity NetBenefits Welcome Brochure</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/a-NetBenefitsMobileFlyer.pdf">Fidelity NetBenefits Mobile Apps Guide</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAny 401K questions can be directed to Joe Grabar or Chris Gure by calling 919-322-2761 or Joe.Grabar@FRPAdvisors.com and Chris.Gure@FRPAdvisors.com\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Health Insurance Base Plan Information</strong></span></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2.1-Blue-Options-Medical-Benefit-HSA-2017.pdf">2017 BCBS Summary of Benefits Coverage- HSA</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Use the form below to change your payroll deduction for your HSA account.</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/hsa-payroll-deduction-and-certification.docx">HSA Payroll Deduction</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">HSA Rollover Information</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://healthequity.com/ed/bcbsnc/" target="_blank">HSA Roll Over</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Health Insurance Buy Up Plan Information</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2.2-Blue-Options-Medical-Benefit-PPO-2017.pdf">2017 BCBS Summary of Benefits Coverage- PPO </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Dental Insurance Information </strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/3-BCBS-Dental-Blue.pdf">2017 BCBS Dental Blue Dental Insurance Information </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Vision Insurance Information</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4-Blue-20-20-Benefit-Summary-2017.pdf">2017 BCBS Blue 20/20</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Medical Enrollment Change Application</strong></span>\r\n\r\nThis form is required to add a dependent or change your address for  your 2017 medical coverage.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Enrollment-Change-Application1.pdf">Medical enrollment Change Application</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Inc.''s disability and life insurance coverage.</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/5-USAble-benefits-Summary-2017.pdf">Sequence, Inc. Usable Life Benefits</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6-Voluntary-Life-Summary-2017.pdf">Voluntary Life Summary 2017</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7-Voluntary-Life-Rates-2017.pdf">Voluntary Life Rates 2017</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8-USAble-Evidence-of-Insurability-Form-for-Voluntary-Life-2017.pdf">USAable Evidence of Inurability Form </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Mass Mutual LTD Disability Buy Up</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10-Mass-Mutual-LTD-Disability-Buy-Up.pdf">Mass Mutual LTD Disability</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>PNC Bank WorkPlace Banking </strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11-PNC-Bank-WorkPlace-Banking.pdf">PNC Workplace banking </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Company Credit Card Login Link</strong></span>\r\n\r\nTo access your Sequence credit card account login here:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://intellilink.spendmanagement.visa.com/secure/welcome.asp" target="_blank">Visa Intellilink Spend Management</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1><span style="text-decoration: underline;">ADP Workforce Now Information</span></h1>\r\n<b>Login URL:</b> <a href="https://workforcenow.adp.com/">https://workforcenow.adp.com/</a>\r\n\r\n<b>Initial Registration Code:</b> SequenceQC-1\r\n\r\n*if prompted to enter Employee ID or SSN, please use the <b>SSN</b> option.\r\n<h1><span style="color: #da202c;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Employee Rights, Labor Law Compliance and e-Verify</span></span></h1>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-hub', '', '', '2016-12-08 12:51:51', '2016-12-08 17:51:51', '', 0, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=226', 0, 'page', '', 0),
