(286, 80, '2016-10-14 09:09:54', '2016-10-14 13:09:54', '<h1>2016 Benefit Information</h1>\r\n2016 benefit information is here! See below for all of the 2016 benefit enrollment/change information. If you have any questions concerning these forms please contact <a href="mailto:cbrown@sequenceqcs.com" target="_blank">Carrie Brown</a> (HR).\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Benefits At A Glance (BAAG)</strong></span>\r\n\r\nThe link below provides an overview of the benefits offered by Sequence Inc.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/a-Sequence-BAAG-2016.pdf">Sequence 2016 BAAG</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Fidelity 401k</strong></span>\r\n\r\nLinks and documentation\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title="Netbenefits" href="https://nb.fidelity.com/public/nb/default/home">401k NetBenefits Link</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/DS-Fidelity-Enrollment-Guide-7-16-15-2.pdf">Fidelity Enrollment Guide</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/a-NBAdvisorBrochure.pdf">Fidelity NetBenefits Welcome Brochure</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/a-NetBenefitsMobileFlyer.pdf">Fidelity NetBenefits Mobile Apps Guide</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAny 401K questions can be directed to Joe Grabar or Jon Dewar by calling 919-322-2761 or Joe.Grabar@FRPAdvisors.com and Jon.Dewar@FRPAdvisors.com\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Health Insurance Base Plan Information</strong></span></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/2016-BCBS-Medical-Summary-of-Benefits-Coverage-HSA-Plan.pdf">2016 BCBS Summary of Benefits Coverage- HSA</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nUse the form below to change your payroll deduction for your HSA account.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/hsa-payroll-deduction-and-certification.docx">HSA Payroll Deduction</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHSA Rollover Information\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://healthequity.com/ed/bcbsnc/" target="_blank">HSA Roll Over</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Health Insurance Buy Up Plan Information</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/2016-BCBS-Medical-Summary-of-Benefits-Coverage-PPO.pdf">2016 BCBS Summary of Benefits Coverage- PPO </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Dental Insurance Information and Enrollment</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Dental-Insurance-Inforamtion-Enrollment.pdf">Dental Insurance Information &amp; Enrollment Form</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Medical Enrollment Change Application</strong></span>\r\n\r\nThis form is required to add a dependent or change your address for  your 2015 medical coverage.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Enrollment-Change-Application1.pdf">Medical enrollment Change Application</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Inc.''s disability and life insurance coverage.</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://New Title Sequence, Inc. Usable Life Benefits">Sequence, Inc. Usable Life Benefits </a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Company Credit Card Login Link</strong></span>\r\n\r\nTo access your Sequence credit card account login here:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="https://intellilink.spendmanagement.visa.com/secure/welcome.asp" target="_blank">Visa Intellilink Spend Management</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Sequence Verizon Discount Information</strong></span>\r\n\r\nSequence employees who ​have ​Verizon accounts​ are now eligible to receive 15% off the monthly access fee on eligible plans and features. You can receive an additional 3% discount on eligible plans and eligible data features by registering with My Verizon and enrolling in paperless billing.\r\n<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top">Go to the <a class="m_-5775526853620629743gmail-m_-2326205298505249746blueLinks" href="http://ecrmomcl.verizonwireless.com/documentmanager/openaccess/EmailHandler/c.do?a=ECRMOM&amp;c=38935&amp;i=CA1C1833-7312-0675-F1FD-790AF62BE3DA&amp;r=MTY1NTAyNzU3MwAwyvmZ5z4u99p4DSRWOPRKYm72ez3KJiRbKnO7sXrUUUOPXaMhRgdVsmcwEqUk%2BiGKoSa%2FrlbyxRHjS%2BTB8GzD&amp;t=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.verizonwireless.com%2Fb2c%2Femployee%2FeleuLanding.jsp%3FEMHID%3Db6f66f4c28afe0ebc20bbe61ee261d0c%26cmp%3DEMC-OM-ELEU" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://ecrmomcl.verizonwireless.com/documentmanager/openaccess/EmailHandler/c.do?a%3DECRMOM%26c%3D38935%26i%3DCA1C1833-7312-0675-F1FD-790AF62BE3DA%26r%3DMTY1NTAyNzU3MwAwyvmZ5z4u99p4DSRWOPRKYm72ez3KJiRbKnO7sXrUUUOPXaMhRgdVsmcwEqUk%252BiGKoSa%252FrlbyxRHjS%252BTB8GzD%26t%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.verizonwireless.com%252Fb2c%252Femployee%252FeleuLanding.jsp%253FEMHID%253Db6f66f4c28afe0ebc20bbe61ee261d0c%2526cmp%253DEMC-OM-ELEU&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1476536678879000&amp;usg=AFQjCNG2FHXt2to3LSQOsGQDAu-sFnhqmA"><span class="m_-5775526853620629743gmail-m_-2326205298505249746outlookFix">Verizon Discount Portal</span></a>.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top">\r\n<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top" width="10"><span style="font-family: ''trebuche