(382, 80, '2014-03-14 21:33:00', '2014-03-15 01:33:00', 'To schedule online meetings using Sequence Inc.''s online meeting tool, GoToMeeting, follow the steps below.\r\n\r\n1. Log into your <a href="https://calendar.google.com/a/sequenceqcs.com">calendar</a> through a web browser.\r\n2. Create your meeting as you normally would any other meeting. Under the Event details tab, on the right hand side, select Rooms, etc. where you would add meeting guests.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/RoomsEtc_Image.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-383 alignnone" alt="RoomsEtc_Image" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/RoomsEtc_Image-300x131.png" width="300" height="131" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. Ensure you check "Show only available". This will show you if the GoToMeeting accounts are available for your meeting. The GoToMeeting accounts are Sequence Compliance (GTM) and Sequence Quality (GTM). Select "Add" for which ever account you would like to use. This will add and book the resource to your meeting.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/ResourceAdded_Image.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-387 alignnone" alt="ResourceAdded_Image" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/ResourceAdded_Image-300x113.png" width="300" height="113" /></a>\r\n\r\n4. Continue to add information to your meeting as needed and save your meeting.\r\n5. Now that you have your meeting scheduled and the online resource booked, you''ll need to schedule the meeting in GoToMeeting to get the online meeting information. Go to <a href="http://www.gotomeeting.com">GoToMeeting </a>and login using the credential for the <strong>resource you just booked to your meeting.</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sequence Compliance</span>\r\nUser name = sequencecompliance@sequenceqcs.com\r\nPassword = #Sequence01!\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sequence Quality\r\n</span>User name = sequencequality@sequenceqcs.com\r\nPassword = #Sequence01!\r\n\r\n6. Select "Schedule a meeting".\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/GTM_Schedule_Image.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-389" alt="GTM_Schedule_Image" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/GTM_Schedule_Image-300x101.png" width="300" height="101" /></a>\r\n\r\n7. Enter the appropriate information ensuring you schedule the same date and time as your meeting scheduled in your Google calendar. Click Schedule at the bottom and capture the online meeting information. You can then either add this information to your Google calendar meeting or simply email it to your participants.\r\n8. Just prior to your online meeting, log back into GoToMeeting with the credentials in which you booked for your meeting and start the meeting.', 'Scheduling Online Meetings With GoToMeeting', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'scheduling-online-meetings-with-gotomeeting', '', '', '2014-04-02 21:18:11', '2014-04-03 01:18:11', '', 418, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=382', 0, 'page', '', 0),
