(564, 80, '2014-07-09 09:33:23', '2014-07-09 13:33:23', 'In order to connect into the Sequence Inc. corporate network while away from the office you will need to obtain VPN access rights (contact Sequence IS) and download and install the VPN client. Instructions on how to install the VPN client are below.\r\n\r\nStep #1: Log into Palo Alto\r\nOpen a browser and go to seqportal.sequenceqcs.com. From there you should see the following screen.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/VPN_SiteSecurityCertificate.png"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-571" alt="VPN_SiteSecurityCertificate" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/VPN_SiteSecurityCertificate-1024x647.png" width="922" height="582" /></a>\r\n\r\nSelect "Proceed anyway". You''ll then be directed to the Palo Alto login page (see below). Enter your user name and password (provided by Sequence IS). <strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStep #2: Download and install GlobalProtect.\r\nOnce you''ve logged in, select the version of GlobalProtect for your machine. Download and install GlobalProtect.\r\n\r\nStep #3: Setup GlobalProtect and Connect to VPN\r\nOnce you have installed GlobalProtect, you''ll need to enter your account information. Enter your user name and password, along with the Portal. The Portal is: 74.219.7.242.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/VPN_Settings.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-570" alt="VPN_Settings" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/VPN_Settings.png" width="643" height="387" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhen you click Apply the application will attempt to connect. Once the VPN connection is made you''ll get the following message:\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/VPN_PACertificate.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-568" alt="VPN_PACertificate" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/VPN_PACertificate.png" width="507" height="372" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nClick Continue and you''re now connected to the Sequence corporate network.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Setting Up & Connecting Via VPN', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'setting-up-connecting-via-vpn', '', '', '2014-07-09 09:33:23', '2014-07-09 13:33:23', '', 418, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=564', 0, 'page', '', 0),
