(132273, 80, '2015-02-13 09:56:06', '2015-02-13 14:56:06', '<a title="Launching Discoverant Client" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=83115">Accessing Discoverant Clients</a> | <a title="Discoverant Database Info" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=83710">Database Connection Info</a> | <a href="mailto:isticket@sequenceqcs.com?subject=Request for Discoverant Access">Request Access</a>\r\n\r\nAll Discoverant systems will be undergoing re-configurations starting on Friday, 13-Feb.\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>CURRENT SYSTEM STATUS</strong></span><strong> </strong>\r\nDiscoverant 4.1 <strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">CLOSED</span></strong><span style="color: #00ff00;"><span style="color: #000000;">\r\n</span></span>\r\n\r\nDiscoverant 4.3 <span style="color: #00ff00;"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>CLOSED</strong></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #00ff00;"><span style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.5em;">Discoverant 5.0 </span><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>CLOSED</strong> </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000;">\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Discoverant', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83595-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-13 09:56:06', '2015-02-13 14:56:06', '', 83595, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?p=132273', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(132274, 80, '2015-02-13 09:57:20', '2015-02-13 14:57:20', 'Sequence is currently running Oracle 11g XE as our RDBMS for Discoverant instances. Currently Discoverant 4.1 and Discoverant 4.3 use a single Oracle XE instance. This instance has been loaded with data originally shown and trained on in the latest Discoverant Hierarchy Development training. Currently only the CTAB data has been loaded.\r\n\r\nTo access the database you will need to download and install <a title="SQL Developer" href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/developer-tools/sql-developer/downloads/index.html" target="_blank">SQL Developer</a>.\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>DATABASE CONNECTION INFORMATION</strong></span><strong> </strong>\r\n\r\nAll databases assigned to Discoverant instances will be re-deployed.\r\n<!--\r\n\r\nAll schemas connect using the following Oracle connection information.\r\n\r\n[table]Hostname, Port, SID\r\nseqserv01.sequenceqcs.local, 1521, xe\r\n[/table]\r\n\r\nThe following schemas are available:\r\n\r\n[table]Schema/User, Password\r\ndisco, sequence\r\nctab_ebr, ctab_ebr\r\nctab_hist, ctab_hist\r\nctab_lims, ctab_lims\r\n[/table]\r\n-->\r\n&nbsp;', 'Discoverant Database Info', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83710-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-13 09:57:20', '2015-02-13 14:57:20', '', 83710, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?p=132274', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
