(137671, 80, '2015-02-17 07:39:17', '2015-02-17 12:39:17', '<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Sequence Inc. currently runs Discoverant 4.1, Discoverant 4.3, and Discoverant 5.0 instances for internal training and troubleshooting purposes. Information on how to connect to Discoverant instances is below. </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5em;">You must be connected to Sequence Inc. corporate network in order to launch a Discoverant Client.</strong>\n\nNotice: Please check the previous page for information on available instances of Discoverant.\n<ol>\n	<li>Open an Internet Explorer browser window and navigate to: <a title="http://corp01vw02.sequenceqcs.local/RDWeb" href="http://corp01vw02.sequenceqcs.local/RDWeb" target="_blank">http://corp01vw02.sequenceqcs.local/RDWeb</a>.</li>\n	<li>A warning page will be displayed, "There is a problem with this website''s security certificate", which is normal. Select "Continue to this website (not recommended)".\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IE_Warning.png"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83460" alt="Site Warning" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/IE_Warning-1024x727.png" width="614" height="436" /></a></li>\n	<li>You''ll be directed to the "Work Resources RemoteApp and Desktop Connection" page.\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Work_Resources_Login.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83451" alt="Work Resources" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Work_Resources_Login-1024x727.png" width="614" height="436" /></a></li>\n	<li>Enter your domain credentials, <strong>ensuring to include the domain prefix with your user name</strong>. So you would enter "sequenceqcs.local\\<em>your domain user name</em>" (without the quotes) and then your domain password.\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Login_Info_Selection.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83452" alt="Login_Info_Selection" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Login_Info_Selection-1024x727.png" width="614" height="436" /></a></li>\n	<li>Select your security level. In most cases you''ll select "This is a private computer" and click "Sign in".</li>\n	<li>Once you''ve logged in to Work Resources, you''ll be directed to the application listings page.\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Application_Listing.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83453" alt="Application_Listing" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Application_Listing-1024x727.png" width="614" height="436" /></a></li>\n	<li>Select the Discoverant Client of your choice by <strong>single </strong>clicking on the appropriate icon. The remainder of these steps assumes a selection of Discoverant 4.1.</li>\n	<li>After selecting your Discoverant Client, you''ll receive a RemoteApp warning. Simply click "Connect".\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/RemoteApp_Publisher_Warning.png"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-83457" alt="RemoteApp_Publisher_Warning" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/RemoteApp_Publisher_Warning.png" width="511" height="340" /></a></li>\n	<li>After clicking on Connect, you should see RemoteApp Connection dialog box.\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/RemoteApp_Connecting.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83456" alt="RemoteApp_Connecting" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/RemoteApp_Connecting.png" width="253" height="152" /></a></li>\n	<li>Once your connection has been made, you''ll receive another warning regarding an "unkown publisher". Simply click "Connect".\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/RemoteApp_Publisher_Warning.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83457" alt="RemoteApp_Publisher_Warning" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/RemoteApp_Publisher_Warning.png" width="307" height="204" /></a></li>\n	<li>After clicking "Connect", you''ll be asked for your domain credentials once more. Enter your password into the dialog box and ensure the proper user name is shown.\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Windows_Security_Credentials.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83458" alt="Windows_Security_Credentials" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Windows_Security_Credentials.png" width="263" height="278" /></a></li>\n	<li>Finally, log into Discoverant with your Discoverant credentials.\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Disco_Login.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83459" alt="Disco_Login" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Disco_Login.png" width="428" height="405" /></a></li>\n</ol>', 'Launching Discoverant Client', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83115-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-02-17 07:39:17', '2015-02-17 12:39:17', '', 83115, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?p=137671', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
