blisher_Warning" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/RemoteApp_Publisher_Warning.png" width="307" height="204" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>After clicking "Connect", you''ll be asked for your domain credentials once more. Enter your password into the dialog box and ensure the proper user name is shown.\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Windows_Security_Credentials.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83458" alt="Windows_Security_Credentials" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Windows_Security_Credentials.png" width="263" height="278" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>Finally, log into Discoverant with your Discoverant credentials.\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Disco_Login.png" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-83459" alt="Disco_Login" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Disco_Login.png" width="428" height="405" /></a></li>\r\n</ol>', 'Launching Discoverant Client', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83115-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-17 07:39:19', '2015-02-17 12:39:19', '', 83115, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?p=137672', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(137673, 80, '2015-02-17 07:41:27', '2015-02-17 12:41:27', 'Sequence employs two (2) separate Oracle 11g XE instances within our environments (see the information below). Source data for CTAB and TPS has been loaded into the corp01vw02 instance of Oracle.\r\n\r\nTo access the database you will need to download and install <a title="SQL Developer" href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/developer-tools/sql-developer/downloads/index.html" target="_blank">SQL Developer</a>.\r\n\r\nPersonal schemas can be created if you would like one. If so, please let Rob H. know.\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>DATABASE CONNECTION INFORMATION</strong></span><strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5em;">[table]Hostname/Oracle Instance, Port, SID, Status\r\n</span>seqserv01.sequenceqcs.local, 1521, xe, <strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">DOWN</span></strong>\r\ncorp01vw02.sequenceqcs.local, 1521, xe, <strong><span style="color: #00ff00;">UP</span></strong>\r\n[/table]\r\n\r\nDiscoverant Schemas\r\n[table]Schema/User, Password, Available on host(s)\r\ndisco5_dev, disco5_dev, corp01vw02.sequenceqcs.local\r\ndisco5_qa, disco5_qa, corp01vw02.sequenceqcs.local\r\ndisco5_prod, disco5_prod, corp01vw02.sequenceqcs.local\r\n[/table]\r\n\r\nCTAB Schemas\r\n[table]Schema/User, Password, Available on host(s)\r\nctab_disco, disco, Both\r\nctab_ebr, ctab_ebr, Both\r\nctab_hist, ctab_hist, Both\r\nctab_lims, ctab_lims, Both\r\n[/table]\r\n\r\nTPS Schemas\r\n[table]Schema/User, Password, Available on host(s)\r\ndemo_disco, disco, Both\r\ndemo_ebr, demo_ebr, Both\r\ndemo_hist, demo_hist, Both\r\ndemo_lims, demo_lims, Both\r\ndemo_primrexport, demo_primrexport, Both\r\n[/table]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Discoverant Database Info', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '83710-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-17 07:41:27', '2015-02-17 12:41:27', '', 83710, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?p=137673', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
