(430226, 80, '2015-09-02 15:19:45', '2015-09-02 19:19:45', 'Hello All,\nBelow is a good event for free beer and food if you are in the RTP area.  Check it out!\nThanks\n\n\nTick. Tock. Time''s running out to "stein up" for FIT''s Oktoberfest. To make sure you don''t miss this fun time, take time to register right now!\n\nFIT''s 4th Annual Oktoberfest takes place in Research Triangle Park at our 12 TW Alexander site on Thursday, September 17 from 5:00 PM to 10:00 PM. This year’s Oktoberfest promises to be our most epic fest yet with more folks, more fun, and more authentic German food and spirits than you can shake a stein at!\n\nDon''t wait! Register to attend this one-of-a-kind event right now.  \n\n\nGet ready... We''ve got kegs of fun on tap for our 4th Annual Oktoberfest. Sign up now to drink in the good times at this authentically German event!\n\nWHEN\nThursday, September 17, 2015 \n5:00 PM - 10:00 PM\n \n\nWHERE \nFIT America\n12 T.W. Alexander Drive, Building 100\nDurham, NC 27709\n\n\n\n\n\nhttp://info.freudenberg-it.com/fitokt15?hsCtaTracking=a665a610-8c61-4dad-b5a5-18f829d2e9b9%7Cb4158eaf-b5e5-469e-ab26-58cc800649c7&utm_campaign=Oktoberfest+2015&utm_medium=email&utm_source=hs_email&utm_content=21716168', 'Free Steins, Beer &amp; Food - OKTOBERFEST !', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'free-steins-beer-food-oktoberfest', '', '', '2015-09-02 15:19:45', '2015-09-02 19:19:45', '', 399595, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?topic=free-steins-beer-food-oktoberfest', 0, 'topic', '', 0),
