(837635, 172, '2016-07-12 14:58:59', '2016-07-12 18:58:59', '[su_spoiler title="Google Hangouts for Meetings (Screenshare/Audio)" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nStart a Conference Call\r\n\r\n1. Open Hangouts at hangouts.google.com or in Gmail.\r\n\r\n2. Select a person from the Hangouts list or search for their name or email address. When you find the person you want, click their name.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908308"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-908308" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search.png" alt="search" width="188" height="214" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. To start a group video call, for each person in your group, type their name and check the box in front of their name.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search-person.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908382"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-908382" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search-person-300x87.png" alt="search person" width="300" height="87" /></a>\r\n\r\n4. Click the video icon .\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/video-button.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908384"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-908384" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/video-button.png" alt="video button" width="261" height="83" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Note:  We found that the video calls really enhanced meetings and has some fun audio/video sound bites (Clapping/laughs) etc., you can play with to break up boring meetings.  You can turn off your camera at any time.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Share your screen</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Open a Hangouts video call.\r\n\r\n2. Place your mouse by the left side of the video call window. A bar with various app icons will appear.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/screenshare.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908391"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-908391" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/screenshare.png" alt="screenshare" width="212" height="118" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. Click the Screenshare icon. (Green one)\r\n\r\n4. Choose whether to share your entire desktop, your browser window, or app.   Click Start share.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Stop sharing your screen at any time by clicking the Screenshare icon.</em>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Google Drive" style="fancy"]<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/google-drive.png" rel="attachment wp-att-911609"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-911609" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/google-drive-300x150.png" alt="google drive" width="300" height="150" /></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Never Lose another work file</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">You can sync your files between your desktop and the web. This means any changes you make to a file on your Mac or PC will automatically show up on the same file at </span><a href="https://drive.google.com/" target="_blank"><b>drive.google.com</b></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Follow instructions to download Google Drive</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2374989?hl=en" target="_blank"><b>https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2374989?hl=en</b></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Collaborate / Review Documents Simultaneously</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Google documents allows two or more people to collaboratively work on a document at the same time.  You can login to google docs at:</span><a href="http://docs.google.com/" target="_blank"> <b>http://docs.google.com/</b></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">More info about collaboration found here:</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DgxWwzBzudoxxu-3tXw6pI8vrAUc5A0sv4hHKKSAPlw/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><b>https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DgxWwzBzudoxxu-3tXw6pI8vrAUc5A0sv4hHKKSAPlw/edit?usp=sharing</b></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Create a Simple Form or Spreadsheet</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">To poll, survey, quiz, or otherwise collect information using a form from a spreadsheet in Google Sheets:</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/87809?hl=en" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://support.google.com/docs/answer/87809?hl=en</span></a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Office Remote Application" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office-remote.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908393"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-908393" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office-remote-300x110.png" alt="office remote" width="300" height="110" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Office Remote is a mobile app for Android users to control PowerPoint presentations, without having to stand at the computer they are presenting from. This app gives you full control of the presentation by: allowing you to start, end, and navigate the presentation, view speaker notes, set a presentation timer,  as well as putting a laser pointer on the screen. It can also be used to navigate Excel and Word documents.\r\n\r\nApp requirements:\r\n- Microsoft Office 2013. This app does not work with Office 2013 RT or earlier versions of Office.\r\n- Bluetooth on your PC\r\n- The desktop add-in for Office Remote must be installed on your PC http://aka.ms/officeremotepc\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.microsoft.office.officeremote&amp;hl=en" target="_blank">Office Remote Download</a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Accessing Google Applications" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n<em>Inside of your Sequence Google account, there are several apps available to you including: Drive, Calendar, Docs, etc. To access these apps, refer to the screenshots below.</em>\r\n\r\nIn the top right hand  corner of the Google page, there will be a grid icon, among others.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/grid-icon.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908387"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-908387" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/grid-icon.png" alt="grid icon" width="194" height="56" /></a>\r\n\r\nAll of the applications Google offers will be located inside of the grid icon.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/apps.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908388"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-908388" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/apps-195x300.png" alt="apps" width="195" height="300" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]', 'Productivity through Google', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'googleproductivity', '', '', '2016-09-02 11:21:57', '2016-09-02 15:21:57', '', 0, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=837635', 0, 'page', '', 0),
