(893172, 172, '2016-07-12 08:56:28', '2016-07-12 12:56:28', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">Setting Up and Connecting Via Virtual Private Network:</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">In order to connect into the Sequence Inc. corporate network while away from the office you will need to obtain VPN access rights (contact Sequence IS) and download and install the VPN client. Instructions on how to install the VPN client are below.  </span>\r\n\r\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/0B85cp9arLK2zcjlMeDVJWWhZZFk/view?usp=sharing\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once you have installed GlobalProtect, you''ll need to enter your account information. Enter your username and password, along with the Portal. </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Portal is: 74.219.7.242</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen you click Apply the application will attempt to connect. Once the VPN connection is made you’ll get a popup message. Click continue and you are now connected to the Sequence corporate network.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Connecting to the Virtual Private Network (VPN)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '837646-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-12 08:56:28', '2016-07-12 12:56:28', '', 837646, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?p=893172', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
