(893546, 172, '2016-07-12 13:29:23', '2016-07-12 17:29:23', '<em><strong>Default voicemail password: 1234</strong></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Headset Setup</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Assemble the headset with desired earpiece attachments.</li>\r\n	<li>Plug the ethernet cable into the back of the phone where the headset symbol is next to it.</li>\r\n	<li>Also, be sure to insert the power cable into the dock and the battery into the back of the headset.</li>\r\n	<li>Once power light is on, proceed to next set of directions for <em>Enabling Headset Use</em>.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<em>Please note: Having too many headsets in one small area can cause interference with the signal and it will have static. </em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Enabling Headset Use</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Go to Options, scroll down to headset type and set it to wireless</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">In Director, this can be set for the user as a primary default by doing following:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Personal Options→Automatic Off Hook - Wireless Headset</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Remote Monitoring</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The direct phone number for the remote monitoring line is: 919-234-1845</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'ShoreTel Phones', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '837346-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-12 13:29:23', '2016-07-12 17:29:23', '', 837346, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?p=893546', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
