(904558, 172, '2016-07-21 13:18:11', '2016-07-21 17:18:11', '[su_spoiler title="Booking a Conference Room" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n<strong>Booking a Conference Room</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">1.In your Sequence issued Google account, go to Calendars.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">2.Click on “Create” in the upper left corner of the screen.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">      -Title the event and set the date and time as needed.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Create-Calendars.png" rel="attachment wp-att-893248"><img class="alignnone wp-image-893248 size-full" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Create-Calendars.png" alt="Create- Calendars" width="524" height="400" /></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">3.On the right side of the screen, there is an option to add guests or rooms.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Guests-Rooms.png" rel="attachment wp-att-893252"><img class="alignnone wp-image-893252 size-full" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Guests-Rooms.png" alt="Guests Rooms" width="302" height="408" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">4.Choose rooms to see what is available in your office for the chosen time.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">5. Add guests to invite the people that you would like to attend. </span>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once everything is filled out, you can then click “Save” at the top of the screen.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Google Hangouts for Meetings (Screenshare/Audio)" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nStart a Conference Call\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Open Hangouts at hangouts.google.com or in Gmail.</li>\r\n	<li>Select a person from the Hangouts list or search for their name or email address. When you find the person you want, click their name.</li>\r\n	<li>To start a group video call, for each person in your group, type their name and check the box in front of their name.</li>\r\n	<li>Click the video icon .</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNote:  We found that the video calls really enhanced meetings and has some fun audio/video sound bites (Clapping/laughs) etc., you can play with to break up boring meetings.  You can turn off your camera at any time.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nShare your screen\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Open a Hangouts video call.</li>\r\n	<li>Place your mouse by the left side of the video call window. A bar with various app icons will appear.</li>\r\n	<li>Click the Screenshare icon .</li>\r\n	<li>Choose whether to share your entire desktop, your browser window, or app.   Click Start share.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStop sharing your screen at any time by clicking the Screenshare icon .\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Google Drive" style="fancy"]<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<b>Never Lose another work file</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">You can sync your files between your desktop and the web. This means any changes you make to a file on your Mac or PC will automatically show up on the same file at </span><a href="https://drive.google.com/" target="_blank"><b>drive.google.com</b></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Follow instructions to download Google Drive</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2374989?hl=en" target="_blank"><b>https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2374989?hl=en</b></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Collaborate / Review Documents Simultaneously</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Google documents allows two or more people to collaboratively work on a document at the same time.  You can login to google docs at:</span><a href="http://docs.google.com/" target="_blank"> <b>http://docs.google.com/</b></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">More info about collaboration found here:</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DgxWwzBzudoxxu-3tXw6pI8vrAUc5A0sv4hHKKSAPlw/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><b>https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DgxWwzBzudoxxu-3tXw6pI8vrAUc5A0sv4hHKKSAPlw/edit?usp=sharing</b></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Create a Simple Form or Spreadsheet</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">To poll, survey, quiz, or otherwise collect information using a form from a spreadsheet in Google Sheets:</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/87809?hl=en" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://support.google.com/docs/answer/87809?hl=en</span></a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Office Remote Application" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nThe Office Remote is a mobile app for Android users to control PowerPoint presentations, without having to stand at the computer they are presenting from. This app gives you full control of the presentation by: allowing you to start, end, and navigate the presentation, view speaker notes, set a presentation timer,  as well as putting a laser pointer on the screen. It can also be used to navigate Excel and Word documents.\r\n\r\nApp requirements:\r\n- Microsoft Office 2013. This app does not work with Office 2013 RT or earlier versions of Office.\r\n- Bluetooth on your PC\r\n- The desktop add-in for Office Remote must be installed on your PC http://aka.ms/officeremotepc\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.microsoft.office.officeremote&amp;hl=en" target="_blank">Office Remote Download</a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Productivity through Google', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '837635-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-21 13:18:11', '2016-07-21 17:18:11', '', 837635, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/gotomeeting', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(904559, 172, '2016-07-21 13:24:06', '2016-07-21 17:24:06', '<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>SUPPORT\r\n</strong></span>You may request support from IS by submitting a support case. Support cases may be submitted via email by emailing  <a href="mailto:isticket@sequenceqcs.com">isticket@sequenceqcs.com</a> or by having your manager submit a case for you in NetSuite.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=887741&amp;preview=true">New Employees Click HERE</a></h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=837640&amp;preview=true">IS Setup</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=837257&amp;preview=true">Office Connectivity</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=837646&amp;preview=true">Connecting to Virtual Private Network</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/googleproductivity">Productivity through Google</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=837644&amp;preview=true">GoTo Meeting</a>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a title="Discoverant" href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=83595">Discoverant</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=837346&amp;preview=true">Shoretel Phones</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/?page_id=837350&amp;preview=true">Windows Basics</a></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Information Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '340-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-21 13:24:06', '2016-07-21 17:24:06', '', 340, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/gotomeeting', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(904560, 172, '2016-07-21 13:25:54', '2016-07-21 17:25:54', '<h1><strong><u>Information Solutions Setup</u></strong></h1>\r\n<strong><u>Email</u></strong>\r\n\r\nYou should have received information to your personal (or secondary) email address giving your password and how to login.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Contact Sequence IS (email:  isticket@sequenceqcs.com) for all issues.</u></strong>\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Company Asset" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nYour laptop has been setup and configured for you. To login use the following credentials:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Domain: Sequenceqcs.local</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>User name: First Initial Last Name (Ex.  mputnam)</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Password: Welcome2016</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Local (non-domain):</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>User name:  Computer name* \\ Consultant</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Password:  Welcome2016</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n*Note:  Computer name can found by clicking the “How Do I Logon to another Domain” at the Other User login window.  This account can be used if domain account locks out etc.\r\n\r\n<strong>Please login and ensure BOTH passwords are changed.</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIt is recommended that you change your password. Your new password should meet the minimum requirements for our network:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Not contain the user''s account name or parts of the user''s full name that exceed two consecutive characters</li>\r\n	<li>Be at least seven characters in length</li>\r\n	<li>Contain characters from three of the following four categories:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>English uppercase characters (A through Z)</li>\r\n	<li>English lowercase characters (a through z)</li>\r\n	<li>Base 10 digits (0 through 9)</li>\r\n	<li>Non-alphabetic characters (for example, !, $, #, %)</li>\r\n	<li>Complexity requirements are enforced when passwords are changed or created.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDomain passwords are required to be changed every 180 days.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nYou are also a “local administrator” to your laptop which gives you the privilege of being able to install applications. If you have any issues attempting to install software please contact Sequence IS by sending email to <a href="mailto:isticket@sequenceqcs.com">isticket@sequenceqcs.com</a>.\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n<u>Mapped drives</u>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sandbox (S:\\)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This is a shared drive in which you can transfer files to coworkers etc. Everyone on the domain has access to this drive and can create and/or delete</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>User (U:\\)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This is your private drive and any data you wish to store here needs to be placed in the folder with your name (e.g. U:\\mputnam). No one but you (and administrators) have access to this drive.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou may have additional mapped drives depending on your security level. Please inquire with IS if you have any questions regarding your mapped drives and access.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<u>Installed Applications</u>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Symantec Cloud Endpoint Protection</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft Office – see below for more information</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<u>Printers</u>\r\n\r\nGo to Start &gt; Type Add Printer &gt; Select Network Printer .  Select the printer closest to you.\r\n\r\n2500 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bizhub West\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Located next to the warehouse doors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n2100 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bizhub (Installed and set as default)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP 10.1.1.212</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP 10.1.1.211</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Microsoft Office</u></strong>\r\n\r\nYou have been granted a Microsoft Office License, Office Pro Plus, which has already been downloaded and installed for you.   Your login will be your sequence email address (if needed).  Please contact <a href="mailto:isticket@sequenceqcs.com">isticket@sequenceqcs.com</a> for password issues.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><u>The HUB</u></strong>\r\n\r\nThe HUB is our employee website which contains company information and updates. You can access it at <a href="http://www.sequenceqcs.com">http://www.sequenceqcs.com</a>; click “Login" at the upper right hand side of the page or go to <a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com">www.sequencegxp.com</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nYour credentials to log into the HUB are:\r\n\r\n<strong>Username: Sequence email address</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Password: Welcome2016</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Building Access &amp; Security</u></strong>\r\n\r\nYour access card will grant you access to the Sequence Inc., main offices in Morrisville. If seated in 2500, please see your manager for the security code and instructions on how to arm and disarm the building security.', 'New Employee', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '887741-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-21 13:25:54', '2016-07-21 17:25:54', '', 887741, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/gotomeeting', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
