(904633, 172, '2016-07-21 13:35:26', '2016-07-21 17:35:26', '<b>[su_spoiler title="Sequence Employees" style="fancy"]</b>\r\n\r\nSequence Corporate network password: <strong>13#Sequence# </strong> (Domain Laptops only)\r\n\r\n<strong>Printing:</strong>\r\n\r\n<em> From Windows Devices and Printers</em>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Add Printer</li>\r\n	<li>Add Network, Wireless or Bluetooth</li>\r\n	<li>The Printer that I want wasnt listed</li>\r\n	<li>Find a printer in the directory, based on location or feature</li>\r\n	<li>The four office Printers will be listed (BizHubs are the large guys / HP’s to be used sparingly).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nPrinters:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2500 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>BizHub West\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.0.1.22</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.0.1.73</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>2100 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bizhub\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.1.1.212</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.1.1.211</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n<b>[su_spoiler title="Guests" style="fancy"]</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Sequence Guest network password:    <b>sequencewifi  </b>(all other devices and guests)</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Printing for Guests:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><b>Email docs to address below:</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b><b>For the HP-2100:  </b><b>uba333odrel79@hpeprint.com</b></b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>For the HP-2500: </b><b>  </b><b>677essy755ibge@hpeprint.com</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n<b>[su_spoiler title="Connecting to the VPN" style="fancy"]</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">In order to connect into the Sequence Inc. corporate network while away from the office you will need to obtain VPN access rights (contact Sequence IS) and download and install the VPN client. Instructions on how to install the VPN client are below.  