(907577, 80, '2016-07-25 21:29:47', '2016-07-26 01:29:47', '<b>[su_spoiler title="Sequence Employees" style="fancy"]</b>\n\nSequence Corporate network password: <strong>13#Sequence# </strong> (Domain Laptops only)\n\nSequence Guest network password:    <strong>sequencewifi  </strong>(all other employee devices [e.g. phones] and guests)\n\n<strong>Printing:</strong>\n\n<em> From Windows Devices and Printers</em>\n<ol>\n	<li>Add Printer</li>\n	<li>Add Network, Wireless or Bluetooth</li>\n	<li>The Printer that I want wasnt listed</li>\n	<li>Find a printer in the directory, based on location or feature</li>\n	<li>The four office Printers will be listed (BizHubs are the large guys / HP’s to be used sparingly).</li>\n</ol>\nPrinters:\n<ul>\n	<li>2500 Office\n<ul>\n	<li>BizHub West\n<ul>\n	<li>IP:  10.0.1.22</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>HP\n<ul>\n	<li>IP:  10.0.1.73</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>2100 Office\n<ul>\n	<li>Bizhub\n<ul>\n	<li>IP:  10.1.1.212</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n	<li>HP\n<ul>\n	<li>IP:  10.1.1.211</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\n[/su_spoiler]\n\n[su_spoiler title="Guests" style="fancy"]\n\nSequence Guest network password:    sequencewifi  (all other devices and guests)\n<ul>\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Printing for Guests:</span>\n<ul>\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;">Email docs to address below:</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>For the HP-2100:  uba333odrel79@hpeprint.com</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li>For the HP-2500:   677essy755ibge@hpeprint.com</li>\n</ul>\n[/su_spoiler]\n\n[su_spoiler title="Connecting to the VPN" style="fancy"]\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">In order to connect into the Sequence Inc. corporate network while away from the office you will need to obtain VPN access rights (contact Sequence IS) and download and install the VPN client. Instructions on how to install the VPN client are below.  </span>\n<ul>\n	<li>Download GlobalProtect to access VPN using this link: <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BzxOFaiAF0HvUUJPVXpBbXlVZ1U/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank">GlobalProtect Download</a></li>\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once you have installed GlobalProtect, you''ll need to enter your account information. Enter your Windows cred, along with the Portal.</span>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Portal is: 74.219.7.242</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\nWhen you click Apply the application will attempt to connect. Once the VPN connection is made you’ll get a popup message. Click continue and you are now connected to the Sequence corporate network.\n\n[/su_spoiler]', 'Office Connectivty', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '837257-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-25 21:29:47', '2016-07-26 01:29:47', '', 837257, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/gotomeeting', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
