(909796, 172, '2016-07-27 08:23:54', '2016-07-27 12:23:54', '[su_spoiler title="Sequence Employees" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nSequence Corporate network password: <strong>13#Sequence# </strong> (Domain Laptops only)\r\n\r\nSequence Guest network password:    <strong>sequencewifi  </strong>(all other employee devices [e.g. phones] and guests)\r\n\r\n<strong>Printing:</strong>\r\n\r\n<em> From Windows Devices and Printers</em>\r\n\r\n1. Add Printer\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/add-a-printer.png" rel="attachment wp-att-909791"><img class="size-full wp-image-909791 alignleft" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/add-a-printer.png" alt="add a printer" width="241" height="83" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n2. Add Network, Wireless or Bluetooth\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/network.png" rel="attachment wp-att-909793"><img class="size-medium wp-image-909793 alignleft" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/network-300x80.png" alt="network" width="300" height="80" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n3. The Printer that I want wasn''t listed\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/not-listed.png" rel="attachment wp-att-909794"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-909794" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/not-listed-300x88.png" alt="not listed" width="300" height="88" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n4. Find a printer in the directory, based on location or feature\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/location.png" rel="attachment wp-att-909792"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-909792" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/location-300x81.png" alt="location" width="300" height="81" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n5. The four office Printers will be listed (BizHubs are the large guys / HP’s to be used sparingly).\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/printers.png" rel="attachment wp-att-909795"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-909795" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/printers-300x131.png" alt="printers" width="300" height="131" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPrinters:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2500 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>BizHub West\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.0.1.22</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.0.1.73</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>2100 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bizhub\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.1.1.212</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP:  10.1.1.211</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Guests" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nSequence Guest network password:    sequencewifi  (all other devices and guests)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Printing for Guests:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;">Email docs to address below:</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For the HP-2100:  uba333odrel79@hpeprint.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For the HP-2500:   677essy755ibge@hpeprint.com</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Booking a Conference Room" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n<strong>Booking a Conference Room</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">1.In your Sequence issued Google account, go to Calendars.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">2.Click on “Create” in the upper left corner of the screen.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">      -Title the event and set the date and time as needed.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Create-Calendars.png" rel="attachment wp-att-893248"><img class="alignnone wp-image-893248 size-full" sr