(957601, 80, '2016-09-02 11:18:24', '2016-09-02 15:18:24', '[su_spoiler title="Email" style="fancy"]\r\nYou should have received information to your personal (or secondary) email address giving your password and how to login. Please ensure that you change your password once logged in.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Contact Sequence IS (email:  isticket@sequenceqcs.com) for all issues.</u></strong>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Company Asset" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nYour laptop has been setup and configured for you. To login use the following credentials:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Domain: Sequenceqcs.local</strong><strong>User name: First Initial Last Name (Ex.  mputnam)</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Password: Welcome2016</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Local (non-domain):</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>User name:  Computer name* \\ Consultant</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Password:  Welcome2016</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n*Note:  Computer name can found by clicking the “How Do I Logon to another Domain” at the Other User login window (as seen below).  This account can be used if domain account locks out etc.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft wp-image-911587 size-medium" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/login-1-268x300.png" alt="login" width="268" height="300" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Please login and ensure BOTH passwords are changed.</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>You are also a “local administrator” to your laptop which gives you the privilege of being able to install applications. If you have any issues attempting to install software please contact Sequence IS by sending email to <a href="mailto:isticket@sequenceqcs.com">isticket@sequenceqcs.com</a>.</em>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Passphrase Maintenance" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nIt is recommended that you change your password. Your new password should meet the minimum requirements for our network:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Not contain the user''s account name or parts of the user''s full name that exceed two consecutive characters</li>\r\n	<li>Be at least seven characters in length</li>\r\n	<li>Contain characters from three of the following four categories:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>English uppercase characters (A through Z)</li>\r\n	<li>English lowercase characters (a through z)</li>\r\n	<li>Base 10 digits (0 through 9)</li>\r\n	<li>Non-alphabetic characters (for example, !, $, #, %)</li>\r\n	<li>Complexity requirements are enforced when passwords are changed or created.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDomain passwords are required to be changed every 180 days.\r\n\r\n<em>You can change your password using "Ctrl + Alt + Delete" bringing you to this screen:</em>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ctrlaltdel.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908561"><img class="size-medium wp-image-908561 alignleft" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ctrlaltdel-300x192.png" alt="ctrl+alt+del" width="300" height="192" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Mapped Drives" style="fancy"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sandbox (S:\\)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This is a shared drive in which you can transfer files to coworkers etc. Everyone on the domain has access to this drive and can create and/or delete</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>User (U:\\)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>This is your private drive and any data you wish to store here needs to be placed in the folder with your name (e.g. U:\\mputnam). No one but you (and administrators) have access to this drive.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou may have additional mapped drives depending on your security level. Please inquire with IS if you have any questions regarding your mapped drives and access.\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Installed Applications" style="fancy"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Symantec Cloud Endpoint Protection</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft Office 365 Business– see below for more information</li>\r\n	<li>FreePDF\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Print to PDF</li>\r\n	<li>Minor PDF editing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/symantec.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-911594"><img class="alignleft wp-image-911594 size-medium" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/symantec-300x186.jpg" alt="symantec" width="300" height="186" /></a><a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office.png" rel="attachment wp-att-911591"><img class="wp-image-911591 size-medium alignnone" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office-300x200.png" alt="office" width="300" height="200" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Printers" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nGo to Start &gt; Type Add Printer &gt; Select Network Printer .  Select the printer closest to you.\r\n\r\n2500 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bizhub West\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Located next to the warehouse doors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n2100 Office\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bizhub (Installed and set as default)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP 10.1.1.212</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>HP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IP 10.1.1.211</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Microsoft Office" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office365.gif" rel="attachment wp-att-911597"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-911597 size-full" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office365.gif" alt="office365" width="600" height="214" /></a>\r\n\r\nYou have been granted a Microsoft Office License, Office 365 Business (unless you need MS Access), which has already been downloaded and installed for you.\r\n\r\n<strong>Username:</strong> <em>Sequence Email</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Password:</strong> <em>Welcome2016</em>\r\n\r\nPlease contact <a href="mailto:isticket@sequenceqcs.com">isticket@sequenceqcs.com</a> for password issues.\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="The HUB" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nThe HUB is our employee website which contains company information and updates. You can access it at <a href="http://www.sequenceqcs.com">http://www.sequenceqcs.com</a>; click “Login" at the upper right hand side of the page or go to <a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com">www.sequencegxp.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/login.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908565"><img class="size-medium wp-image-908565 alignleft" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/login-300x82.png" alt="login" width="300" height="82" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nYour credentials to log into the HUB are:\r\n\r\n<strong>Username: Sequence email address</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Password: Welcome2016</strong>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Building Access and Security" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nYour access card will grant you access to the Sequence Inc., main offices in Morrisville.\r\n\r\n2100 Gateway Centre Boulevard, Suite 301\r\nMorrisville, NC 27560\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The normal operating hours for this building are 6am- 6pm. Your access card will be needed to enter the building outside of these hours.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n2500 Gateway Centre Boulevard, Suite 850\r\nMorrisville, NC 27560\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If seated in 2500, please see your manager for the security code and instructions on how to arm and disarm the building security.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_spoiler]', 'Information Solutions Setup', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '887741-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-02 11:18:24', '2016-09-02 15:18:24', '', 887741, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/gotomeeting', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(957602, 80, '2016-09-02 11:21:57', '2016-09-02 15:21:57', '[su_spoiler title="Google Hangouts for Meetings (Screenshare/Audio)" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\nStart a Conference Call\r\n\r\n1. Open Hangouts at hangouts.google.com or in Gmail.\r\n\r\n2. Select a person from the Hangouts list or search for their name or email address. When you find the person you want, click their name.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908308"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-908308" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search.png" alt="search" width="188" height="214" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. To start a group video call, for each person in your group, type their name and check the box in front of their name.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search-person.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908382"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-908382" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/search-person-300x87.png" alt="search person" width="300" height="87" /></a>\r\n\r\n4. Click the video icon .\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/video-button.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908384"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-908384" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/video-button.png" alt="video button" width="261" height="83" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Note:  We found that the video calls really enhanced meetings and has some fun audio/video sound bites (Clapping/laughs) etc., you can play with to break up boring meetings.  You can turn off your camera at any time.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Share your screen</strong>\r\n\r\n1. Open a Hangouts video call.\r\n\r\n2. Place your mouse by the left side of the video call window. A bar with various app icons will appear.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/screenshare.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908391"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-908391" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/screenshare.png" alt="screenshare" width="212" height="118" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. Click the Screenshare icon. (Green one)\r\n\r\n4. Choose whether to share your entire desktop, your browser window, or app.   Click Start share.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Stop sharing your screen at any time by clicking the Screenshare icon.</em>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Google Drive" style="fancy"]<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/google-drive.png" rel="attachment wp-att-911609"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-911609" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/google-drive-300x150.png" alt="google drive" width="300" height="150" /></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Never Lose another work file</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">You can sync your files between your desktop and the web. This means any changes you make to a file on your Mac or PC will automatically show up on the same file at </span><a href="https://drive.google.com/" target="_blank"><b>drive.google.com</b></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Follow instructions to download Google Drive</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2374989?hl=en" target="_blank"><b>https://support.google.com/drive/answer/2374989?hl=en</b></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Collaborate / Review Documents Simultaneously</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Google documents allows two or more people to collaboratively work on a document at the same time.  You can login to google docs at:</span><a href="http://docs.google.com/" target="_blank"> <b>http://docs.google.com/</b></a>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">More info about collaboration found here:</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DgxWwzBzudoxxu-3tXw6pI8vrAUc5A0sv4hHKKSAPlw/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank"><b>https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DgxWwzBzudoxxu-3tXw6pI8vrAUc5A0sv4hHKKSAPlw/edit?usp=sharing</b></a>\r\n\r\n<b>Create a Simple Form or Spreadsheet</b>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">To poll, survey, quiz, or otherwise collect information using a form from a spreadsheet in Google Sheets:</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="https://support.google.com/docs/answer/87809?hl=en" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://support.google.com/docs/answer/87809?hl=en</span></a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Office Remote Application" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office-remote.png" rel="attachment wp-att-908393"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-908393" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/office-remote-300x110.png" alt="office remote" width="300" height="110" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Office Remote is a mobile app for Android users to control PowerPoint presentations, without having to stand at the computer they are presenting from. This app gives you full control of the presentation by: allowing you to start, end, and navigate the presentation, view speaker notes, set a presentation timer,  as well as putting a laser pointer on the screen. It can also be used to navigate Excel and Word documents.\r\n\r\nApp requirements:\r\n- Microsoft Office 2013. This app does not work with Office 2013 RT or earlier versions of Office.\r\n- Bluetooth on your PC\r\n- The desktop add-in for Office Remote must be installed on your PC http://aka.ms/officeremotepc\r\n\r\n<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.microsoft.office.officeremote&amp;hl=en" target="_blank">Office Remote Download</a>\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Accessing Google Applications" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n<em>Inside of your Sequence Google account, there are several apps available to you including: Drive, Calendar, Docs, etc. To access these apps, refer to the screenshots below.</em>\r\n\r\nIn the top right hand  corner of the Google page, there will be a grid icon, among o