(1057867, 205, '2016-11-22 13:34:26', '2016-11-22 18:34:26', '<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/logo-nerd-glasses.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1052879" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/logo-nerd-glasses.jpg" alt="logo-nerd-glasses" width="247" height="182" /></a>\r\n\r\nAt Sequence, we work with our clients to understand the unique requirements of their facility in order to develop a cost effective method to meet functional and quality objectives associated with new facilities, existing facility expansions, shutdowns, and system upgrades. We have quality project resources that have experience in following industries: From concept through implementation, Sequence, Inc. has the expertise you need.\r\n\r\nThe vast experience of our personnel provides great perspective and insight into strategies for implementing practical and compliant solutions pertaining to commissioning and integration of control systems, facility start up, processes, and equipment. In addition, we guarantee facility qualification consistent with the evolving harmonized regulatory framework around risk and science-based approaches to regulatory compliance. Our clients across the US, Canada, and beyond benefit from our industry-leading approach tailored around planning, management, document generation, and project execution. We are committed to product safety and efficacy through alignment with our client partners to ensure compliance of their regulated facilities.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #da202c;">Our Services </span></strong>\r\nWe offer a wide range of services at Sequence and take pride in our expertise and diverse skill sets. We have the resources and expertise to add value to all of your project needs from start to finish. Sequence is always evolving our service offerings to meet ever changing client needs, and yet maintaining a level of service to our client that is second to none. Se