(1058079, 205, '2016-11-22 13:34:26', '2016-11-22 18:34:26', '<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/logo-nerd-glasses.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1052879" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/logo-nerd-glasses.jpg" alt="logo-nerd-glasses" width="247" height="182" /></a>\r\n\r\nAt Sequence, we work with our clients to understand the unique requirements of their facility in order to develop a cost effective method to meet functional and quality objectives associated with new facilities, existing facility expansions, shutdowns, and system upgrades. We have quality project resources that have experience in following industries: From conceptthrough implementation, Sequence, Inc. has the expertise you need.\r\n\r\nThe vast experience of our personnel provides great perspective and insight into strategies for implementing practical and compliant solutions pertaining to commissioning and integration of control systems, facility start up, processes, and equipment. In addition, we guarantee facility qualification consistent with the evolving harmonized regulatory framework around risk and science-based approaches to regulatory compliance. Our clients across the US, Canada, and beyond benefit from our industry-leading approach tailored around planning, management, document generation, and project execution. We are committed to product safety and efficacy through alignment with our client partners to ensure compliance of their regulated facilities.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #da202c;">Our Services </span></strong>\r\nWe offer awide range of services at Sequence and take pride in our expertise and diverse skill sets. We have the resources and expertise to add value to all of your project needs from startto finish. Sequence is always evolving our service offerings to meet ever changing client needs, and yet maintaining a level of service to our clientthatis second to none. Sequence can support you in all aspects ofthe following services\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Services" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n• Automation Engineering &amp; Validation\r\n• Equipment/Utilities Validation\r\n• Equipment Commissioning\r\n• Building Systems Commissioning\r\n• FAT/SAT Support\r\n• Technical Writing\r\n• Risked Based Verification (ASTM 2500e)\r\n• Manufacturing Support Start-Up\r\n• Functional &amp; Design Specification Development\r\n• Design Reviews\r\n• Tech Transfers\r\n• Decommissioning\r\n• Process Validation\r\n• Manufacturing Process Intelligence\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\nWe have quality project resources that have experience in following industries:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Engineering & Technical Services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1057867-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-22 13:34:26', '2016-11-22 18:34:26', '', 1057867, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/gotomeeting', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1058927, 205, '2016-11-23 10:55:17', '2016-11-23 15:55:17', '<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/155418768.jpg"><img class="alignright wp-image-299 size-medium" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/155418768-300x200.jpg" alt="155418768" width="300" height="200" /></a>Sequence, Inc. provides a scalable and customizable monitoring solution for your temperature, humidity, CO2, or pressure monitoring needs. Whether you have controlled incubators containing your critical stability samples, low temperature freezers containing valuable cell banks or biologics, or refrigerators used for day-to-day operations, our Sequence Monitoring Center is capable of providing personalized around the clock support to ensure materials are maintained under your specified conditions.\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Monitoring Capabilities" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n• Cold Chain\r\n• Stability Chamber\r\n• Facility\r\n• Environmental\r\n• Plasma Donor Centers\r\n• Blood Banks\r\n• Food Storage\r\n• Cargo\r\n• Data Centers\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\nOur Services:\r\nThe Sequence Monitoring Center supports clients across all 50 states and is experienced in the installation, configuration, calibration, validation, quality oversight, and monitoring support of your product, equipment, and/or facility. Through our client dedicated support module, our 24 hour call center, and our ability to provide vendor management, quality oversight and remediation, we are able to provide our clients a complete solution for monitoring support and compliance.\r\n\r\nIn addition, the Sequence Monitoring Center provides customized data analysis and reporting to help turn raw data into meaningful information. Sequence will work with you to define your reporting and trending needs to ensure you get the information required to meet your project demands.\r\n\r\nThe data transmitted to our Monitoring Center is constantly assessed for alarms or issues that could adversely impact your product or manufacturing environment. Early detection of an adverse trend can make the difference in avoiding potential product loss, saving you valuable time and money. At the first sign of trouble, a Monitoring Center Specialist notifies you of the situation, immediately initiating the investigation process. It doesn’t end there, as Sequence Specialists will work with you throughout the investigation process to determine the scope of the alarm and evaluate the impact to the product or environment. Sequence Quality Assurance is available to review all data to ensure data integrity, results are accurately represented, and to provide guidance through the closure of event remediation.\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler title="Services We Provide" style="fancy"]\r\n\r\n• Dedicated Support\r\n• Validation Documentation\r\n• Deviation Resolution\r\n• Customized Data Analysis\r\n• Adverse Trend Notification\r\n• Calibration\r\n• Trend Reporting\r\n• Quality Oversight\r\n• Alarm Notification\r\n• Vendor Management\r\n• Validation Execution\r\n• Dedicated Support Module\r\n• Investigations\r\n• Adverse Trend Remediation\r\n• Out of Calibration Reports\r\n\r\n[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Monitoring Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'monitoring-services', '', '', '2016-12-07 13:36:53', '2016-12-07 18:36:53', '', 0, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?post_type=kbe_knowledgebase&#038;p=1058927', 0, 'kbe_knowledgebase', '', 0),
