content/uploads/2016/07/name-your-meeting.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1064437" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/name-your-meeting.png" alt="name-your-meeting" width="515" height="88" /></a>\r\n<ol start="4">\r\n 	<li>On the right side of the page, select "Rooms", and add Sequence Quality or Sequence Compliance,\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Guests-Rooms-Added.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-893253" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Guests-Rooms-Added.png" alt="Guests Rooms- Added" width="313" height="290" /></a></li>\r\n 	<li>Select "Find a time" to view the calendar and book a time..\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Find-a-time.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-893255" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Find-a-time.png" alt="Find a time" width="669" height="154" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Available-Times.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-893256" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Available-Times.png" alt="Available Times" width="1585" height="521" /></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ol start="6">\r\n 	<li>After selecting your time Click back on Event Details tab\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/6.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1064445" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/6.png" alt="6" width="673" height="191" /></a></li>\r\n 	<li>Create your meeting in GoToMeeting\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Click Sign In\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/7.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1064440" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/7.png" alt="7" width="673" height="191" /></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>In the pop up window use the appropriate sign in information for the GoToMeeting account you will be using\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Start-1.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-1064443 size-medium" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Start-1-300x253.png" alt="start-1" width="300" height="253" /></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAccount information:\r\n\r\nAccount 1: Sequencequality@sequenceqcs.com\r\n\r\nPW #Sequence01!\r\n\r\nAccount 2: Sequencecompliance@sequenceqcs.com\r\n\r\nPW #Sequence01!\r\n\r\n9. Click Sign in\r\n\r\n10. Clicking Add will Create your meeting and generate the link for your meeting.\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/7.3.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1064439" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/7.3.png" alt="7-3" width="513" height="166" /></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/8.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1064441" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/8.png" alt="8" width="651" height="417" /></a>\r\n\r\n11.Save your Meeting\r\n<a href="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/name-your-meeting.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1064437" src="http://www.sequencegxp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/name-your-meeting.png" alt="name-your-meeting" width="515" height="88" /></a>\r\n\r\n12. Start Your Meeting\r\n\r\nPlease Note: Your meeting <u>HAS</u> to be started from APP not from invite link that is sent out\r\n\r\nPlease Note: Your meeting <u>HAS</u> to be started from APP not from invite link that is sent out\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Download the GoToMeeting desktop application\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><a href="https://download.citrixonline.com/launcher2/launch.html?product=g2m&amp;endpointParams=%7B%22EGWPort%22%3A%2280%2C443%2C8200%22%2C%22Action%22%3A%22Host%22%2C%22EGWAddress%22%3A%22216.115.208.230%22%2C%22BAT%22%3A%227070948639474970886las9hwJijpSVVXvH5ffG3qOFdGBmQFf%22%2C%22BrokerServiceSuffix%22%3A%22%40ISL1%22%2C%22Build%22