(1071176, 205, '2016-12-05 09:10:09', '2016-12-05 14:10:09', '<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="color: #da2000; text-decoration: underline;">We have extensive experience with laboratory instrument qualification, method validation, and tech transfers</span></strong></span>\r\n\r\nSequence, Inc. has extensive experience validating analytical equipment, instruments, and methods for the Biopharma and Medical Device industries.\r\n\r\nWith each quality and compliance effort, our consultants begin with an initial consideration of the technical complexity of the lab system, degree of customization, and intended use by our client. This allows us to implement an effective, risk-based approach during each equipment or instrumentation validation effort. Testing performed by Sequence consultants provides documented evidence that the system is installed properly, performs accurately, and produces reliable data.\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="color: #da2000;">Laboratory Equipment Systems Experience</span></strong>\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">• Centrifuges                    • Isolators\r\n• Refrigerators                 • Robotic Pipettors\r\n• Freezers                          • Stability Chambers\r\n• Incubators                     • Ovens\r\n• Water Baths                  • Vessels\r\n• Autoclaves                     • Tanks\r\n• Cold Rooms</p>\r\n<strong><span style="color: #da2000;">Laboratory Instrument Systems Experience</span></strong>\r\n\r\n•DNA Characterization Systems                                            • HPLC\r\n• Microbial Detection &amp; Identification Systems                 • UPLC\r\n• Microplate Readers • Viable Cell Counters                       • GC\r\n• Microscope Camera Systems                                               • LCMS\r\n• Real-Time PCR Systems                                                       • Capillary Electrophoresis Systems\r\n• Particle Counters                                                                   • FT-IR\r\n• Spectrophotometers                                                              • Fluorometers\r\n• SEC-MALLS                                                                            • Nephelometers\r\n• TOC Analyzers                                                                        • Cyanide Analyzers\r\n• Titrators                                                                                   • Gel Chip Analyzers\r\n• Densitometers                                                                        • Polarimeters\r\n• Atomic Absorption Systems\r\n\r\nPast projects include retrospective legacy validation initiatives (including an initial gap analysis), prospective/concurrent validation of individual systems, prospective validation of laboratory startups, laboratory relocation, new product/product changeover testing enhancements, laboratory decommissioning, electronic data retention/archival initiatives and much more.', 'Laboratory Compliance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'laboratory-compliance', '', '', '2016-12-05 09:10:09', '2016-12-05 14:10:09', '', 0, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?post_type=kbe_knowledgebase&#038;p=1071176', 0, 'kbe_knowledgebase', '', 0);
