(1071178, 205, '2016-12-05 09:13:03', '2016-12-05 14:13:03', '<strong><span style="color: #da202c;">Let our team integrate and support a range of software products that achieve compliance for your site.</span></strong>\r\n\r\nSequence system implementation and support model services are unsurpassed in the Biotechnology and Pharmaceutical industries. We strive for a hands-on, customer-first approach for software system implementation, validation and support that ensures customer systems are qualified, maintained and supported at the highest standard. Our expertise is utilized in authoring client Standard Operating Procedures and Work Instructions for use, maintenance and administration of computerized systems.\r\n\r\nOur Software Management Services team is experience in implementation, validation and support of both small and large-scale manufacturing, laboratory and operational support systems such as:\r\n<p style="padding-left: 30px;">•  Process Analytics / Manufacturing Intelligence\r\n• Enterprise Resource Planning\r\n• Laboratory Sample Management\r\n• Deviation and CAPA\r\n• Maintenance Management\r\n• Learning Management / Training Delivery</p>\r\n<strong><span style="color: #da202c;">Software Consultants Skilled &amp; Knowledgeable in Discoverant, Noverant™ &amp; More</span></strong>\r\n\r\nAt Sequence, Inc., we are involved from development to production support for Discoverant manufacturing intelligence platform. This Process Management Informatics (PMI) Sotfware utilizes data from existing system data stores to perform extensive analysis and help improve yield and lower costs. Additionally, we have partnered with Noverant™, and now offer a customized cloud-based training solution that we can implement and support for our clients nationwide.\r\n\r\nMany of our software management consultants are certified in the systems we validate and support, including LMS and Discoverant software.\r\n\r\nIn addition to commercially available software solutions, our software consultants have been involved with the development and implementation of custom client solutions. With our systems validation, implementation, configuration and support services, Sequence, Inc. can be your end-to-end solutions partner.', 'Software Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'software-management', '', '', '2016-12-05 09:13:03', '2016-12-05 14:13:03', '', 0, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/?post_type=kbe_knowledgebase&#038;p=1071178', 0, 'kbe_knowledgebase', '', 0),
