gh Quality Program development, our team can identify the keys areas for improvement to maximize efficiency as well as reduce the implementation impact to your business.\n\nPAI Readiness\nThe seasoned consultants at Sequence, Inc. are prepared to assist clients in assessing the readiness level for a pre-approval inspection (PAI). Performing mock inspections is a key tool in the process of preparation for inspection by various regulatory bodies.\n\nQA Review &amp; Support\nOur multi-industry expertise gives our consultants a unique perspective on Quality Assurance and can provide innovative solutions for all of your QA needs.', 'Quality Programs & Compliance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1071180-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-12-05 09:34:04', '2016-12-05 14:34:04', '', 1071180, 'http://www.sequencegxp.com/gotomeeting', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
